Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身體!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,溫暖的身體!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:30.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回去吧 艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:33.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:27.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙果然厲害...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 又扔下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對不會讓你跑掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 從昨天開始你就一直在趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去還沒到目的地你就累趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬼現在怎樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺他那惡狠狠的眼神和倔強的性格跟格斯你很像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:54.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止急停!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要多為宿主著想一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一位老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別來無恙呢 掙扎者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是精靈嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶著有趣的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:20.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 這個人似乎...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,久違了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這種地方幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃向那些非人者尋仇之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾要前往之地有何物你自然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近有使徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說 是元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神之手...那些傢伙就在那裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:49.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也夢見了「光之鷹」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是啟示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:58.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以「鷹」為號的某人物將會出現在這塵世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹...你是說鷹?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,羊群被引至沾滿鮮血的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們所追尋的希望乃是「光之鷹」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,力場超過臨界之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本應存在於神之領域的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會千年一度地受肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:22.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你和那位姑娘將會置身其中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如舊日噩夢重演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蝕...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如蝕再臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說那情景...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那場景...會再次出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悅?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:57.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,憑人類的力量無法更改這個祭典的情節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來會出現倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是由失去光芒的太陽所籠罩之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,投射至遙遠人世間的倒影罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想說結果和那時候一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等出乎意料地在此地相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是最好的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等已在因果循環當中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼倒影 什麼因果 我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我的確借助過你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我會憑自己的力量救她出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:41.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或許你身上的烙印會是你的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給你一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一心不可二用!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 到底在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的團長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拍那個摩茲古斯的馬屁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好佩服她的虔誠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 她會聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何那麼愚鈍的傢伙能成為紋章官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是馬屁拍得好唄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說又增加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼增加了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請...請問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一起過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正要去禮拜堂找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令您受驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們幾個因為醜陋的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了殘酷的迫害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被趕出了村子 城市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作為妖怪人忌諱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至有因此逃進森林當野人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是天生的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這副面具的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我全身就會被燒得腐爛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那副樣子恐怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...已經沒個人形了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:15.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 感謝您賜予我這次相遇的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被選中的命運之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自豪而虔誠地活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不喜歡這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對傷害他人這種事情實在喜歡不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可即使如此我也為之自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:35.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是神賜予我的神聖職責
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個聲音是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是禮拜的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅弄出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在頂禮膜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚各做五百次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,五體投地這種膜拜方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這十年間摩茲古斯大人從未有一天間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎禮拜完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是法爾納塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人 您流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 讓您見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這座塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以前關押著被霸王加爾塞利克幽禁的賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,據說他們在所有拷問中不斷向神控訴王罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於感動了上蒼 令天使降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是靈驗非凡的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:40.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以令我下意識地大力禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傷害我幾乎走不動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是不能周圍跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:53.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我很珍視這份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的神聖使命是執行嚴格的神之律法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或許應該為之感到悲哀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:03.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這會為許多人帶來痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傷對我來說既是懲戒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也是信仰的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼迷惑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個任務到底能否拯救民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:22.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,庶民對我們的風評滿是惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕您笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們聖鐵鎖騎士團裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不少人對這個任務持有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以把這番話當作是不成熟之人說的胡話盡情嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心這樣下去只會一味讓恐怖蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人心疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能因任務艱巨而嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能質疑神明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便身心俱疲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦要一心一意 為了神而活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是所謂的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,皆是為了神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆為了神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆為了神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老是承蒙你照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老奶奶 記得不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行啊 搞得渾身髒兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮...妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,約阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是什麼身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你明知道但還是想上我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,客人!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你說再多的甜言蜜語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這...我並沒有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來上我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的有那份勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚午夜鐘聲響起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在河邊等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大清早的嚷那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你愛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:11.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能跟我一起下地獄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是買賣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 我們下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那個孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...幻覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 一起逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰女神啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:53.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來 約阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,山羊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請幫他改宗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來 喝了它你就是我們的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,約阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了那個男人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他想告密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼高不可能活命了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到喧鬧可能會有人來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 你怎麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過來 不要過來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你那是什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:33.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我從以前就討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,裝作無所不知的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對他人擺出高高在上的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好讓自己感覺良好並沉沒其中對吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也跟我一樣是個娼婦而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何能如此瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我大聲叫喚的話同伴就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你會被大卸八塊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個傻女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...將約阿希姆...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒記錯的話 是妮娜那裏的娼婦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是染病的瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:50.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 讓我們看看那張腐爛的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把繃帶解了一看美的簡直讓人想咬住不鬆口啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 鬧吧鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這才有樂子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,餓死我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:58.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔女!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,點火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,服了那個女人 還真敢幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:02.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,團長家以前似乎是獵殺邪教徒的火刑場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小小年紀就開始放火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被批准搜捕黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也是因為三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她在法王廳逮捕了企圖發動叛亂的邪教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:17.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...並全部處予火刑的功績
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是經過千錘百煉的那啥(鐵石心腸)啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然應該離她遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的人 不准說閒話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:25.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是邪教徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,邪教徒的兒子也是邪教徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要證明不是你就把火把扔過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,審問他父親的時候已經調查清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:48.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是...是我失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想有恩於你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:05.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喲!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒記錯你是傑羅姆男爵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.46,0:22:13.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是紋章官 記性真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不是那麼壞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:17.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:20.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很有騎士風範哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這件事事關我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和那個孩子有相同的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:33.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母親也以邪教徒的罪名處予火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:36.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前 就在我的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:41.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:06.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:07.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給她祝福!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請賜予她神明的祝福!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個頭腦簡單四肢發達的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...我終於追上你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:50.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:09.20,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,她是個虔誠的孩子!
